short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deletes all of your Instagram photos at once.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enter the number of Instagram photos you want to delete. The current version can delete 10 photos in batch at once. If you want to delete more than 10 photos, you need to click the plugin again separately. 

Steps: 

1. Download and install the plugin.
2. Log in to your Instagram account and open your profile. 
3 Hold down the F12 , enter the Inspect Element, and then switch to the Mobile Mode.
4. Click the plugin icon and enter the number of Instagram photos you want to delete. 

PS: Be sure to click the plugin icon on your profile.
